    "This process could exploit the potentialities of TL since building managers and operators can pre-determine, given a target building, the best source building from which to transfer a DRL-based control policy.",
    "-Developing an infrastructure to explore the implementation of the online TL methodology in a real-world testbed.",
    "Transfer Learning is a machine learning approach aimed at leveraging previously acquired knowledge in one task to enhance performance in a different yet related problem (Pinto et al. 2022c).",
    "This method involves sharing knowledge at the initial stages of the learning process, which expedites the convergence of machine learning models compared to starting from scratch without any prior knowledge.",
    "As stated in Pan and Yang (2010) and Pinto et al. (2022c), TL enhances the learning of a predictive function in the target domain D T, associated with task T T, by leveraging the knowledge gained from the source domain D S with task T S."
